'desc': [u'

Piyo Piyo Finger Toothbrush (Transparent) Price: Rs.115

When your baby develops their first teeth you have to be extra careful about their oral hygiene. Parents must ensure that their baby’s teeth are clean and must use a soft and gentle toothbrush to do this. The Piyo Piyo Finger Toothbrush is an ideal toothbrush to use on your baby’s delicate teeth and gums.

This baby toothbrush from Piyo Piyo has grade A silicone bristles that are soft and gentle on your baby’s teeth. The rounded design of the toothbrush ensures that the brush does not bruise during brushing. You can easily slip the toothbrush on your finger and gently massage your baby’s teeth
column13:
gums and tongue. The soft massaging action is also helpful in easing discomfort that may arise from budding teeth. The Piyo Piyo silicone finger toothbrush is heat and cold resistant ( -20 degree centigrade up to 120 degree centigrade) and can be steam sterilized or boiled for maximum hygiene. This finger toothbrush from Piyo Piyo helps keep your baby\u2019s mouth healthy and also helps establish the oral hygiene regimen from an early age.

\n
\n ']
